{
  "texts": [
    "These extracted tuples are transformed into word vectors using pre-trained GloVe method (Pennington et al. 2014) that extracts only meaningful words.",
    "The vector is fed into the LSTM network as an input.",
    "The output from the LSTM network is fed into hidden layers connected with two perceptrons, which uses softmax activation function that serves as an output to the prediction model.",
